data.description: Welcome to your next investment opportunity! This stunning corner lot home is a rare find, offering not only a beautiful residence but also a tenant already in place, making it a seamless transition for any savvy investor seeking immediate cash flow.    Situated in the highly sought-after city of Cibolo, this two-story gem boasts two spacious living areas and exquisite custom touches throughout, creating an inviting and cozy atmosphere. The convenience of being close to shopping and major highways adds to the appeal of this prime location.    Whether you're looking to expand your investment portfolio or start one with a reliable income stream, this property offers the perfect opportunity. Don't miss out on this chance to own a piece of Cibolo's charm while enjoying the benefits of a smart investment choice. Welcome home!
